          "reviewBody": "I visited the school for my daughter’s admission and was so impressed with the look and feel of the campus and the way spacious classrooms have been designed keeping in mind the child’s learning and their needs. Curriculum is well planned. As they say “slow and study wins the race” is what they believe in.",
