            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Heritage Xperiential Learning School GCE is everything we could have hoped for in an educational institution for our child. The school not only emphasizes academic excellence but also fosters character development and social-emotional well-being. The teachers are experienced, compassionate, and talented at engaging students in meaningful learning experiences. The school also implements innovative teaching techniques and uses the latest technology to enhance learning. The collaboration between parents, teachers, and administrators is outstanding, ensuring that the educational journey is a joint effort.",
